Before submitting a new issue, make sure to do the following:

1. Install the latest Agent:
   https://github.com/UltimateHackingKeyboard/agent/releases/latest
2. Use Agent to update to the latest firmware:
   https://github.com/UltimateHackingKeyboard/firmware/releases/latest
3. If your issue is UHK 80 specific, state your connection type (USB, BLE, or dongle) and whether the keyboard halves are connected with the bridge cable.
4. Our contact form will suggest solutions, so copy-paste your message at https://ultimatehackingkeyboard.com/contact-us - Please don't post customer support issues here.
